PRIVACY-POLICY

This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which ritaiacibelli collects, uses, maintains and discloses
information collected from users (each, a "User") of the games developed by ritaiacibelli ("Games") available on
Google Play. This Privacy Policy applies to all Games offered by ritaiacibelli.

Information we collect

We may collect device information and approximate location data from Users in order to provide better user
experiences in our Games. We do not collect any other personal information.

Third-party SDKs

Our Games may use third-party software development kits (SDKs), such as Facebook SDK and AppsFlyer SDK, to
collect certain data for the purposes of marketing and analytics. This data may include, but is not limited to,
device information, advertising identifiers, IP address, and gameplay data. The data collected by third-party
SDKs is subject to their own privacy policies, which you can review on their respective websites.

Sharing your personal information

We do not sell, trade, or rent Users personal identification information to others. We may share generic
aggregated demographic information not linked to any personal identification information regarding visitors and
users with our business partners, trusted affiliates and advertisers for the purposes outlined above.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

ritaiacibelli has the discretion to update this Privacy Policy at any time. When we do, we will revise the
updated date at the bottom of this page. We encourage Users to frequently check this page for any changes to
stay informed about how we are helping to protect the personal information we collect. You acknowledge and agree
that it is your responsibility to review this Privacy Policy periodically and become aware of modifications.

Your acceptance of these terms

By using our Games, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this Privacy
Policy, please do not use our Games. Your continued use of our Games following the posting of changes to this
Privacy Policy will be deemed your acceptance of those changes.

Contacting us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, the practices of our Games, or your dealings with our
Games, please contact us at the following email address: ritaiacibelli@gmail.com.
